release.title: Horace Silver and the Jazz Messengers

annotation.text:
Recorded on November 13, 1954 (Tracks 1-3 & 8) and February 6, 1955 (Tracks 4-7) at the Van Gelder Studio, Hackensack, New Jersey 

Remastered in 2004 by Rudy Van Gelder

Originally issued as BLP 1518 in 1956
